ini and it=\r\ns rise. Just do sadhana, overcome\n your&lt;BR&gt;&gt; weaknesses and improve your=\r\n detachment over time. Again, I want to emphasize that detachment is not di=\r\nsgust or distaste for life/things/people around you. Disgust is the other s=\r\nide of coin of attachment. It is a negative attachment.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&nb=\r\nsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;Don&#39;t worry about &lt;BR&gt;&gt; whether you=\r\nr Kundalini rises or not. Worry about whether you are able to resist 6 inte=\r\nrnal enemies (shadripus) and 8 bondages (ashta pashas) or &lt;BR&gt;&gt; not. If =\r\nyour ability to resist them is increasing, you are making progress. EVEN IF=\r\n your Kundalini is fast asleep, you are still making progress. When you com=\r\npletely overcome them, Kundalini (your self-awareness) &lt;BR&gt;&gt; will automa=\r\ntically ascend to the top and meet Her Lord (true Self).&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&n=\r\nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&nbsp;&nb=\r\nsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;=\r\nOne word on surrendering to\n a personal deity. Though true surrender is hel=\r\npful, most people do not have it. They simply do business with god. Though =\r\npeople may be offended by my words, this is the plain and bare fact.&lt;BR&gt;&gt=\r\n; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&quot;I want X, I will pray to you and please g=\r\nive it to me&quot;, &quot;I am scared of Kundalini rise, I will pray to you and pleas=\r\ne protect me&quot; - all this is just a business deal. There is something you wa=\r\nnt and you ask god for it. True surrender has no place for agendas, desires=\r\n, demands or expectations. True surrender is losing oneself in one&#39;s fascin=\r\nation for the qualities of Lord. True surrender is accepting anything Lord =\r\nthrows one&#39;s way (whether it is pleasurable or highly painful) as Lord&#39;s pr=\r\nasad and accepting it gratefully. True surrender is thinking of Lord with f=\r\nascination and pleasure, even in the face of (and during) Death.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &g=\r\nt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;If one without true surrender and with many de=\r\nsires and wrong\n notions experiences a Kundalini rise, one may still be tra=\r\npped, despite thinking of a personal god. It is not that god does not want =\r\nto &quot;protect&quot; one as said below. It is not about protecting or endangering. =\r\nIf you go back to my &quot;chipmunk glued to mouse trap&quot; example above, I was tr=\r\nying to protect it, but it was scared. Similarly, one&#39;s conditioning makes =\r\none *run away* from God&#39;s&lt;BR&gt;&gt; protection! God&#39;s protection may seem to =\r\na conditioned mind like grave danger that one should run away from!&lt;BR&gt;&gt;=\r\n &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=\r\n *&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&g=\r\nt; &gt;&gt;Whether through the path of wisdom or surrender, develop dispass=\r\nion and detachment. Realize that all this is temporary and can be taken awa=\r\ny anytime. Enjoy it while you have and keep doing your best, but be prepare=\r\nd to lose everything anytime. Only detachment and a very light mental condi=\r\ntioning\n (very light desires, dislikes etc) can protect one as one&#39;s Kundal=\r\nini rises to meet True Self. Heavy conditioning and impurities in one&#39;s nad=\r\nis will distract rising Kundalini (self-awareness) and stop Her from meetin=\r\ng True Self.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;The real key is how lig=\r\nht your conditioning is.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;Best regard=\r\ns,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;--------&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;Astro=\r\nlogy &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.or=\r\ng/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://www.v